{"tid":1150940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[逢9] 中國農民哭泣！豬瘟沒救 「無敵蟲災」快速擴散11省","createTime":"2019-05-12T08:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T02:40:32.000Z","uid":35070,"like":253,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"55747f9da70f0547d06b8c20b1bdcbe6f8aceb75","tid":1150940,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpKuH5WZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpKuH5WZ.jpg&h=af177789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「秋行軍蟲」（Fall Armyworm，草地貪夜蛾）已侵入亞洲。（路透資料照）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2787496?fbclid=IwAR3gDRnDuPdhoVGapD7MCKmcsCe0mG2vXVpbzA1RDfcdDNX6gWN1SJ8DnkY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2787496%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3gDRnDuPdhoVGapD7MCKmcsCe0mG2vXVpbzA1RDfcdDNX6gWN1SJ8DnkY&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNWwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=46c29aa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2787496%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3gDRnDuPdhoVGapD7MCKmcsCe0mG2vXVpbzA1RDfcdDNX6gWN1SJ8DnkY&h=8a779a7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2787496?fbclid=IwAR3gDRnDuPdhoVGapD7MCKmcsCe0mG2vXVpbzA1RDfcdDNX6gWN1SJ8DnkY</a><br />\n<br />\n2019-05-12 07:27<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國的非洲豬瘟疫情嚴重，現在連香港也失守，此時此刻中國又爆發重大蟲災，惡名昭彰的「秋行軍蟲」（Fall Armyworm，草地貪夜蛾）已迅速擴散到11省區，速度遠遠超過預期。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，今年1月中國雲南省首次發現草地貪夜蛾，截至5月8日，已有雲南、廣西、廣東、貴州、湖南、海南、福建、浙江、湖北、江西、四川等11省（區）、52個市（州）、230個縣（市、區）的玉米受害。<br />\n<br />\n草地貪夜蛾是聯合國糧農組織（FAO）全球預警的重要農業害蟲，可危害80多種植物，食量大，繁殖能力強，遷飛擴散快，幾乎沒有天敵，並對許多農藥有抗藥性。<br />\n<br />\n這種害蟲原在美洲的熱帶和亞熱帶地區，是玉米的重大危害，嚴重時可造成毀種絕收。2016年初首次入侵非洲西部成災，2018年對非洲造成經濟損失高達10到30億美元，玉米毀種面積達5到6%，2018年7月首次傳入亞洲地區。<br />\n<br />\n草地貪夜蛾已在中國境內定殖且建立種群，擴散快、為害大、監控困難，專家預料，夏季以後，蟲災從華南玉米區向長江中下游、黃淮、華東、東北和西北等地蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n中國目前面臨貿易戰、非洲豬瘟，再加上嚴重害蟲，恐使農作物短缺，危及食品供應。"},{"pid":"1133f342086f8921a9dbf93f84f75410a18827de","tid":1150940,"uid":5715,"like":219,"dislike":2,"score":217,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"佢地食唔食草架，驚大陸人民無草食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ce7c242fbb2e9fe42d9ed707a3c918531aae5a","tid":1150940,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eab81df251f14364892f803698c0041e23564ca","tid":1150940,"uid":52595,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"389cd3470f3f2eca3841d46e19001da5ae199c2d","tid":1150940,"uid":46849,"like":140,"dislike":0,"score":140,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"d 蟲可能好味又補呢<br />\n食到佢絕種都得啦"},{"pid":"db6416cc0bdcbfddca3db3e1a885ca248818f2fd","tid":1150940,"uid":31389,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"天啟四騎士又出動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc928248904b56ebee4860db2ea684bf0ed20ad4","tid":1150940,"uid":44454,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"新菜式:秋行軍蟲麻辣燙"},{"pid":"3b72999c302a2bdcf7fac462e5be7e0a7b62d025","tid":1150940,"uid":35070,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"389cd3470f3f2eca3841d46e19001da5ae199c2d","tid":1150940,"uid":46849,"like":140,"dislike":0,"score":140,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"d 蟲可能好味又補呢<br />\n食到佢絕種都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"壯陽補身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90616bffa0a94967a33622e15f0cc3f4fb10ef89","tid":1150940,"uid":8478,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"389cd3470f3f2eca3841d46e19001da5ae199c2d","tid":1150940,"uid":46849,"like":140,"dislike":0,"score":140,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08: